query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS customers (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  customerNumber VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  customerType ENUM('individual', 'company') NOT NULL,
  businessType ENUM('retail', 'wholesale', 'distributor', 'direct') NOT NULL,
  firstName VARCHAR(255),
  lastName VARCHAR(255),
  email VARCHAR(320),
  phone VARCHAR(50),
  companyName VARCHAR(500),
  taxId VARCHAR(100),
  website VARCHAR(500),
  billingAddress JSON,
  shippingAddress JSON,
  googlePlaceId VARCHAR(255),
  latitude DECIMAL(10,8),
  longitude DECIMAL(11,8),
  source VARCHAR(100),
  externalIds JSON,
  tags JSON,
  notes TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX email_idx (email),
  INDEX company_idx (companyName)
)
